title: Ryan Chitwood
text: Ryan Chitwood is a Quantitative Analyst at Synovus. Before that he was the Research & Data Analyst at PAEA. plotthedata is his personal website and portfolio. Each post is a recreation of a past project he worked on. In his spare time, Ryan enjoys playing basketball and hanging out with his family.
